### Database Layer (Prisma + SQLite)

#### [NEW] `prisma/schema.prisma`
Data models:

```prisma
model Customer {
  id          String    @id @default(cuid())
  fullName    String
  email       String
  phone       String
  createdAt   DateTime  @default(now())
  voucher     Voucher?
}

model Voucher {
  id          String    @id @default(cuid())
  code        String    @unique
  customerId  String    @unique
  customer    Customer  @relation(fields: [customerId], references: [id])
  status      String    @default("ACTIVE")   // ACTIVE | USED | EXPIRED
  usedAt      DateTime?
  branchId    String?
  branch      Branch?   @relation(fields: [branchId], references: [id])
  createdAt   DateTime  @default(now())
  expiresAt   DateTime?
}

model Branch {
  id          String    @id @default(cuid())
  name        String
  location    String?
  vouchers    Voucher[]
}

model Admin {
  id          String    @id @default(cuid())
  username    String    @unique
  password    String                          // bcrypt hashed
}
```

#### [NEW] `prisma/seed.ts`
Seeds branches and an initial admin account.

