    ADMIN["🔐 Admin Login\n(/gate/secret-hash)"] --> DASH["📊 Dashboard"]
    DASH --> ANAL["📈 Analytics\n(Charts, Stats)"]
    DASH --> REDEEM["🔍 Redeem Voucher\n(Code + Branch)"]
    REDEEM --> API2["⚡ POST /api/admin/vouchers/redeem"]
    API2 --> DB
    ANAL --> API3["⚡ GET /api/admin/analytics"]
    API3 --> DB
```

